## What NOT To Do

- Client photography still pending тАФ Unsplash stand-ins (each marked with an HTML comment) are approved placeholder treatment; swap them for client assets when confirmed. Do not present stand-ins as final imagery.
- Never guess at open client decisions тАФ use placeholder + HTML comment
- Never use real FANUC logo тАФ badge usage rights unconfirmed
- Never change CSS load order
- Never hardcode brand colors outside `tokens.css`
- Navigo weights 500/600/800 are NOT available in the kit тАФ use 400 or 700 only